org.eclipse.incquery.patternlanguage.patternLanguage

Interface CompareConstraint

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Constraint, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompareConstraintImpl

    public interface CompareConstraint
extends Constraint
    A representation of the model object 'Compare Constraint'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Left Operand
    • Feature
    • Right Operand

    See Also:
